title: Elite Preseason All State - Fourth Team
text:
Elite Preseason All State - Fourth Team Luke Feddersen IowaPreps.com Editor 
One of the most popular features on Iowa Preps is our preseason All State basketball teams. We take an in-depth look at the entire state and name our elite fourth team All State. See which of the elite athletes around Iowa made the cut as we take a look towards a winter full of hoops! 
Elite Preseason All State - Fourth Team Canyon Hopkins, Earlham
